{"tid":468172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廿幾歲人都仲係沉迷social既垃圾","createTime":"2017-11-14T06:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T02:14:03.000Z","uid":126293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc353765cc8c551bc28905c4d305275db37e2a5c","tid":468172,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"不得不說...社交浪費左我人生入面好大部分既時間...小弟20出頭, 有個六年半既女友, 讀書個陣唔識諗, 由朝到晚都係到社交social, 再加上因為有女, 所以基本都唔會打機, 即使直到上年畢左業出黎做野, 第一份工每日返工放工都照樣social, even因為公司成日都無人, 所以過份到會係上連登9up...去到宜家第2份工, 個人先好似開始醒緊, 家陣我盡量都自制最多都係每日天開一個post... 但其實都覺得每日哂差不多1個鐘時間係一樣根本無回報既野真係好on9...有無人可以幫下我手戒左佢, 或者過來人既經驗分享?<br />\n<br />\nbtw小弟既9up數據: 總留言7876次, 連登續生涯2277日..我哂左咁多時間換到D咩對我人生有意義既野, 我都真係講唔出.."},{"pid":"cf3f2bb8acd60df1a9ffe9e8e6723e62f96afbca","tid":468172,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9992d69847f2249652f5d755fadb24fa314ad08f","tid":468172,"uid":10621,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> social 係上連登開post 唔怪得你話哂時間"},{"pid":"309b86e0736a7e30ebe3265cd61985173c208fdd","tid":468172,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> social 係上連登開post 唔怪得你話哂時間</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480369da5492e7eda2cf3e7918c7dcfdcccf4ef6","tid":468172,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> social 係上連登開post 唔怪得你話哂時間</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as